author: Klas Stolpe
title: Photo: Under The Lights
text:
Photos KLAS STOLPE | JUNEAU EMPIRE Ketchikan senior Nate Fousel and Juneau-Douglas junior Cody Weldon battle in the Brandon Pilot Invitational Wrestling Tournament at Thunder Mountain High School on Saturday. Fousel won by decision. A slideshow of tournament photos is online at juneauempire.com By Klas Stolpe JUNEAU EMPIRE
